  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"padding:0px 0px 15px;margin:0px 0px 25px;border-bottom-color:black;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-bottom-width:3px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:60px;line-height:1;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">⚙️</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">ANTHROPIC ENGINEERING</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:900;font-size:28px;line-height:1.2;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如何为 Agent 构建工具</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"> \n     <br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"> \n    </span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Anthropic 刚刚发布了一篇很值得阅读的文章<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(246, 195, 68); font-weight: bold; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">《</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(246, 195, 68); font-weight: bold; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如何为 Agent 构建工具</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(246, 195, 68); font-weight: bold; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">》</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，包括：如何编写高质量的工具和评估，以及如何利用 Claude 来为自己优化工具，从而提升性能。</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(246, 195, 68); font-weight: bold; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本文是对内容重点的介绍</span>，更多详细信息，可阅读原文</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/writing-tools-for-agents</span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 30px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:8px 15px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;font-size:20px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">什么是工具?</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:15px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">传统软件是确定性系统，而像 Agent 这样的系统是非确定性的。工具是一种新型软件，它反映了确定性系统与非确定性 Agent 之间的契约。我们编写工具时，需要为 Agent 而不是为其他开发者或系统来设计。我们的目标是通过工具，让 Agent 能够采用多种成功策略，扩大其解决各类任务的有效范围。</span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 30px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:900;font-size:24px;line-height:1.1;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 193, 7); visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如何编写工具</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:15px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本文描述了一个与 Agent 协作编写和改进工具的迭代流程：首先构建一个快速原型并进行本地测试，然后通过全面的评估来衡量后续的改动，并与 Agent 一起重复评估和改进的过程。</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_4bc823\" alt=\"Tool building evaluation cycle\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-backw=\"524\" data-backh=\"295\" data-imgfileid=\"100021730\" data-original-style=\"max-width:100%;border:2px solid #ddd;margin:20px 0;border-radius:4px;width:100%;\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_eb9e60\" _width=\"100%\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 627px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 25px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:18px;align-items:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;display:inline-flex;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border-radius:50%;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:30px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;height:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">构建原型</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">快速构建工具原型，亲身体验。使用 Claude Code 编写工具时，提供相关软件库、API 的文档会有帮助。将工具包装在本地 MCP 服务器或 DXT 中，以便在 Claude Code 或 Claude 桌面应用中连接和测试。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:18px;align-items:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;display:inline-flex;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border-radius:50%;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:30px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;height:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">运行评估</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">通过运行评估来衡量 Claude 使用工具的效果。评估任务应基于真实世界用例，并具有足够的复杂性。强大的评估任务可能需要多次（甚至数十次）工具调用。在评估中，我们建议收集准确率、运行时间、工具调用次数、Token 消耗和错误等指标。</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px 0px 0px 15px;margin:20px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-left-color:rgb(255, 193, 7);font-size:13px;border-left-width:3px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们内部 Slack 工具在留出测试集上的性能表现 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_a926c3\" alt=\"Slack tools performance graph\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-backw=\"508\" data-backh=\"286\" data-imgfileid=\"100021729\" data-original-style=\"max-width:100%;border:1px solid #ddd;margin-top:10px;width:100%;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_661354\" _width=\"100%\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.6px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px 0px 0px 15px;margin:20px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-left-color:rgb(255, 193, 7);font-size:13px;border-left-width:3px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们内部 Asana 工具在留出测试集上的性能表现 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_91cba5\" alt=\"Asana tools performance graph\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-backw=\"508\" data-backh=\"286\" data-imgfileid=\"100021732\" data-original-style=\"max-width:100%;border:1px solid #ddd;margin-top:10px;width:100%;\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_593929\" _width=\"100%\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.6px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"></span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:18px;align-items:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;display:inline-flex;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border-radius:50%;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:30px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;height:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">与 Agent 协作</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Agent 是你发现问题和提供反馈的得力伙伴。你可以让 Agent 分析评估结果并为你改进工具。将评估 Agent 的对话记录粘贴到 Claude Code 中，Claude 擅长分析这些记录并一次性重构大量工具。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 30px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 20px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:900;font-size:24px;line-height:1.1;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(242, 101, 34);padding:2px 10px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">编写高效工具的原则</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 25px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原则一: 选择合适的工具</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">更多的工具并不总是带来更好的结果。Agent 的“上下文”有限，应避免返回大量无关信息。应构建少量、有思想、针对特定高影响力工作流的工具。例如，实现一个&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">search_contacts</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;而不是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">list_contacts</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;工具。工具可以整合功能，将多步操作合并为一次调用。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原则二: 为工具命名空间</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当工具功能重叠或目的模糊时，Agent 可能会混淆。使用命名空间（例如&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">asana_search</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">,&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">jira_search</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">）可以帮助在大量工具之间划定界限，帮助 Agent 在正确的时间选择正确的工具。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原则三: 从工具返回有意义的上下文</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">工具应只返回高信号信息，优先考虑上下文相关性而非灵活性。避免使用 UUID 等底层技术标识符，多使用自然语言名称。可以通过&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">response_format</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;枚举参数让 Agent 控制返回“简洁”还是“详细”的响应。</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">详细响应示例 (206 tokens):</span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_9d2583\" alt=\"Detailed tool response\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100021731\" data-original-style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin-top: 5px;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_c3df5b\" _width=\"677px\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 605.375px !important;\"></span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">简洁响应示例 (72 tokens):</span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_da4840\" alt=\"Concise tool response\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37777777777777777\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100021733\" data-original-style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin-top: 5px;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_fa224b\" _width=\"677px\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 605.375px !important;\"></span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原则四: 优化工具响应的 Token 效率</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">优化上下文的数量和质量同样重要。为可能消耗大量上下文的工具响应实现分页、过滤和截断等机制。如果截断响应或出现错误，应提供清晰、可操作的改进建议来引导 Agent。</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">截断响应并提供指导:</span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_c43a8b\" alt=\"Truncated tool response\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6055555555555555\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100021735\" data-original-style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin-top: 5px;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_ce7acb\" _width=\"677px\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 605.388px !important;\"></span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">无帮助的错误 vs 有帮助的错误:</span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040325_2ae12d\" alt=\"Unhelpful error response\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3814814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100021736\" data-original-style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_90a330\" _width=\"677px\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 605.362px !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_60997b\" alt=\"Helpful error response\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100021737\" data-original-style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250912040324_07bf91\" _width=\"677px\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 605.375px !important;\"></span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原则五: 对工具描述进行提示工程</span>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是最有效的方法之一。编写工具描述时，要像向新同事解释一样，将隐含的背景信息明确化。避免模糊性，对预期输入和输出进行清晰描述和严格定义。例如，使用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">user_id</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;而不是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">user</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;作为参数名。对工具描述的微小改进都能带来显著的性能提升。</span>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:20px 0px 0px;margin:25px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-top-width:3px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;border-top-color:black;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">展望未来</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:15px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为 Agent 构建有效的工具，需要我们将软件开发实践从确定性模式转向非确定性模式。有效的工具是有意图且清晰定义的，能明智地使用 Agent 上下文，并能直观地帮助 Agent 解决真实世界的任务。通过系统性、评估驱动的方法，我们可以确保随着 Agent 能力的增强，它们使用的工具也能同步发展。</span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Anthropic 发布实用指南，详细阐述了为 AI Agent 构建高效工具的迭代流程和五项关键原则，旨在优化 Agent 性能和任务解决能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Anthropic 发布实用指南，详细阐述了为 AI Agent 构建高效工具的迭代流程和五项关键原则，旨在优化 Agent 性能和任务解决能力。",
  "summary": "本文是对 Anthropic《如何为 Agent 构建工具》一文的重点介绍。文章首先将工具定义为确定性系统与非确定性 Agent 之间的契约，强调工具设计应以 Agent 为中心，以拓展其解决任务的有效范围。接着，文章描述了一个迭代式工具开发流程：从快速构建原型和本地测试开始，通过基于真实用例的全面评估来衡量工具效果，并利用 Agent 分析评估结果以进行持续改进。文章还提出了编写高效工具的五项核心原则：选择高影响力工具而非越多越好；使用命名空间避免混淆；返回有意义、高信号的上下文信息；优化工具响应的 Token 效率，包括分页、过滤和提供有帮助的错误提示；以及对工具描述进行细致的提示工程，明确化输入输出。这些原则共同指导开发者将传统软件开发思维转向适应非确定性 Agent 的模式，确保工具与 Agent 能力同步发展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "工具是确定性系统与非确定性 Agent 之间的契约，需为 Agent 而非开发者设计",
      "explanation": "理解 Agent 的非确定性特性，工具设计需聚焦于帮助 Agent 扩大其解决任务的有效范围，而非传统软件的确定性交互模式。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建 Agent 工具应遵循迭代式开发流程：原型、评估、Agent 协作改进",
      "explanation": "通过快速原型验证、基于真实用例的全面评估，并利用 Agent 自身分析评估结果来优化工具，形成持续改进的闭环。"
    },
    {
      "point": "高效工具需遵循五大原则，包括工具选择、命名、上下文、Token 效率和提示工程",
      "explanation": "这些原则指导开发者构建精简、清晰、高效且易于 Agent 理解和利用的工具，从而显著提升 Agent 的性能和可靠性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "工具是一种新型软件，它反映了确定性系统与非确定性 Agent 之间的契约。",
    "我们的目标是通过工具，让 Agent 能够采用多种成功策略，扩大其解决各类任务的有效范围。",
    "Agent 是你发现问题和提供反馈的得力伙伴。你可以让 Agent 分析评估结果并为你改进工具。",
    "更多的工具并不总是带来更好的结果。Agent 的\"上下文\"有限，应避免返回大量无关信息。",
    "编写工具描述时，要像向新同事解释一样，将隐含的背景信息明确化。避免模糊性，对预期输入和输出进行清晰描述和严格定义。"
  ],
